Package com.github.wuic.xml

This package provides the classes which read the 'wuic.xml' path.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
FileXmlContextBuilderConfigurator Represents a configurator based on XML read from an URL.
ReaderXmlContextBuilderConfigurator Represents a configurator based on XML read from a Reader.
XmlBuilderBean Represents a builder (engine, DAO) in wuic.xml file.
XmlContextBuilderConfigurator This configurator implements XML supports for WUIC.
XmlHeapBean This class describes the XML representation of a NutsHeap.
XmlPropertyBean Represents a property to be set in a GenericBuilder.
XmlWorkflowBean This class corresponds to the XML representation of a Workflow.
XmlWorkflowTemplateBean This class corresponds to the XML expression of a workflow template with a set of engines to compote the chains of responsibility and the store DAO.
XmlWuicBean Represents the root element in wuic.xml file.
 

Package com.github.wuic.xml Description

This package provides the classes which read the 'wuic.xml' path.
